## Part 5: Evaluation & Success Metrics
Define how the success of the AI-powered music discovery system will be measured:
- **Precision of Semantic Search**: Accuracy of matching user queries to appropriate track characteristics.
- **Catalog Coverage**: Increase in the number of unique artists/tracks surfaced compared to standard recommendations.
- **User Adoption & Retention**: Click-through rates on discovery playlists, repeat usage of the AI assistant, and reduction in track-skip rates.